<span id="freeTextContainer12508116321239445047">I&apos;m really not sure what to say about this book. Was it suppose to be a scary story about a ghost because if it was, I didn&apos;t get it. Maybe it was suppose to be a romantic love story but if it was, I didn&apos;t get it. Overall, it was pretty tedious and in the end, for me, if wasn&apos;t a scary or romantic story.</span>
  <span id="freeText12508116321239445047" style="display:none">I'm really not sure what to say about this book. Was it suppose to be a scary story about a ghost because if it was, I didn't get it. Maybe it was suppose to be a romantic love story but if it was, I didn't get it. Overall, it was pretty tedious and in the end, for me, if wasn't a scary or romantic story.</span>
