<div id="review_41372490" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/41372490" />
    <a title="TheKBSeries" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1188194-thekbseries"><img alt="TheKBSeries" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1211856805p2/1188194.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/41372490?book_show_action=true">Dec 30, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="TheKBSeries" class="user" itemprop="url" name="TheKBSeries" href="/user/show/1188194-thekbseries">TheKBSeries</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audio CD 9789626341186" href="/book/show/1818498.The_Phantom_of_the_Opera">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer41372490" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10510984089558105682">This book changed my life...I&apos;m so not kidding. I saw the play years before I decided to read this book. I&apos;m so sorry that I waited so long because it was fantastic! I plan to re-read it again! It has everything in it! It&apos;s scary, creepy, romantic, sweet, sexy, dark, sad, depressing, etc. This is the third book on my list that I would recommend to anyone that i meet! (having harry potter and the twilight series at number one and two spots. haha) <br/><br/>W A R N I N G *MAY be a spoiler in this next parag</span>
  <span id="freeText10510984089558105682" style="display:none">This book changed my life...I'm so not kidding. I saw the play years before I decided to read this book. I'm so sorry that I waited so long because it was fantastic! I plan to re-read it again! It has everything in it! It's scary, creepy, romantic, sweet, sexy, dark, sad, depressing, etc. This is the third book on my list that I would recommend to anyone that i meet! (having harry potter and the twilight series at number one and two spots. haha) <br /><br />W A R N I N G *MAY be a spoiler in this next paragraph*<br />I love the phantom! He was dark and mysterious. He was that bad guy that you always wanted to love. I do not agree with Christine Daae's choice in the end. I hate who she chose, but yes, i know...it was the better choice.<br /><br />This story remains so dear to my heart. I can relate to almost every character and I truly love the phantom. His intentions were good and he had a good heart...just a bad temper and a bad reason for murder. All he wanted was Christine's love...</span>
  <a data-text-id="10510984089558105682" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
